# Day 9: Biological Databases and APIs — Data Setup
# Run: bl run init.bl
# Creates gene list and variant annotation files with real biological data.
# Works fully offline — no API calls required.

# Source: COSMIC Cancer Gene Census (Sondka et al., Nat Rev Cancer, 2018)
# Source: ClinVar (Landrum et al., Nucleic Acids Res, 2018)
# Coordinates: GRCh38/hg38

print("Day 9: Biological Databases and APIs")
print("=====================================")
print("Generating data files with real cancer driver genes...")
print("")

mkdir("data")

# ============================================================
# 1. Gene list: 25 cancer driver genes with Ensembl IDs,
#    chromosome locations, and functional descriptions
# ============================================================

