    "TP53,ENSG00000141510,17,7668402,7687550,−,Tumor protein p53; guardian of the genome; most mutated gene in human cancer",
    "BRCA1,ENSG00000012048,17,43044295,43170245,−,BRCA1 DNA repair associated; hereditary breast/ovarian cancer",
